{"word":"ἄθυτος","slug":"ἄθυτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄθυτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θύω'><el>θύω1</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>not offered</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>neglected</i>, <el>ἱερὰ ἄθ.</el>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>sacra inauspicata</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>without sacrificing</i>, <el>ἄθυτος ἀπελθεῖν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}